stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_receive: receive transaction tx
    q_receive --> q_check: gas_limit = tx.gasLimit
    q_check --> q_reject: gas_limit > 16777216
    q_check --> q_accept: gas_limit <= 16777216
    q_reject --> [*]: reject tx (MAX_GAS_LIMIT_EXCEEDED)
    q_accept --> [*]: add tx to txpool
